# Human-edited direct dependency manifest for Lunarscout.
#
# Keep this file limited to dependencies imported by the current library,
# tests, native bridge, or checked-in examples. Do not carry Lunar Analyst
# application dependencies here unless Lunarscout starts importing them.
#
# Python osgeo/GDAL bindings are intentionally not installed. Rasterio is the
# supported direct Python GDAL-facing package and must match an available GDAL
# runtime on the target system.

